      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHILL OUT PLATE (6) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.4 lengths at Horsham in a handy 23.82 beating Offensive Lady. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. One of the key runners again. SHE REBEL (4) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at Warrnambool over 450m behind Doongalla Rocket (26.06) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Should play a prominent role. CONQUER (3) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 2.75 lengths (24.31). Strong form has emerged from his last run. Has the ability to give this a shake. PINE BLUFF (8) comes into calculations after placing most recently.",
